author: The Linux Foundation
description:
This week in open source: things are moving fast and in all directions.
CNCF and Synadia resolve a high-stakes governance dispute, OpenSearch keeps shipping, and the PyTorch Foundation expands its mission. Meanwhile, we’ve got new standards emerging, trust frameworks evolving, and mapping tech getting a serious speed boost.

Catch the key moves in under a minute watch this week’s LF Quick Hits.
#OpenSource #PyTorch #OpenSearch #CNCF #AI
title: Open Source Just Leveled Up – Here’s What’s New!
